summary:
This Mod add female follower
in Moorside INN, Morthal.
Her name is Anuschka.
descriptionHtml:
[font=Comic Sans MS][color=#ff0000][size=6]Attention!![/size][/color]
[size=3][color=#ff0000]I don't support this file anymore.....
Actually I'm retired.
However U can download this file, but your own risk. Thank you[/color]

[color=#e06666]Thanks for Downloading my follower mod.[/color]

[color=#e06666]It meaning of Gracious.[/color]

[color=#e06666]This is standalone follower mod.

[color=#a64d79][size=4]Installation[/size][/color][color=#e06666] [/color]

[color=#e06666]     Please use NMM or other Mod manager
     If you don't use them, all my files extract to your Skyrim data folder.
     and active my esp with Skyrim Launcher. [/color]

[color=#a64d79][size=4]Uninstallation[/size][/color]

[color=#e06666]     Also please use NMM or other Mod manager.
     If you don't use them, simply delete all my files.[/color]
